Package: CovariateSearcher
Type: Package
Title: Stepwise Covariate Modeling with NONMEM/bbi Integration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Functional R package for automated stepwise covariate modeling (SCM) 
    with NONMEM integration via bbi/bbr. Provides complete SCM workflow automation,
    parallel model execution, statistical evaluation, automatic recovery from
    estimation failures, and comprehensive progress monitoring.
